    "description": "<strong>Piecewise</strong> is a tool for assembling (literally!) <strong>Discord</strong>, <strong>Mastodon/Pleroma/Misskey</strong>, and <strong>Matrix</strong> chat bots (with more platforms planned in the future!) using a friendly puzzle-like format.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702210/extras/288f3437919528bd4997ea2afcdb1743.webp?t=1692825750\" width=104 height=26 /></span><br>Skip confusing syntax and dive right into logic. Piecewise provides a friendly and familiar interface - even to beginners - based on a visual scripting framework.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702210/extras/8a5296c4e21396d1c7c23b0cf3da891e.webp?t=1692825750\" width=76 height=26 /></span><br>Thanks to Piecewise's large coverage of the platform tools it uses, you'll have full control of a lot of the features you'd expect from a bot written from scratch.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702210/extras/1c814c7a88abbade3b43daf91a1615b2.webp?t=1692825750\" width=109 height=26 /></span><br>Create bridges from one platform to another, or make your bot play nice with everyone: the possibilities are endless.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702210/extras/bfb63ee8e3c07eb542ffae4b9038fbca.webp?t=1692825750\" width=85 height=26 /></span><br>Write an interesting function? Share it with the world using the &quot;Share Blocks&quot; feature, or turn to the community to find functions to add to your bots.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702210/extras/2b3f94b941cd0f4219420cb828be7de6.webp?t=1692825750\" width=84 height=26 /></span><br>Purchase extension packs or make your own to plug into services that provide rich data.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702210/extras/7f55fb454ec587d272d21ffb017201aa.webp?t=1692825750\" width=183 height=26 /></span><br>Ready for prime time? Easily export and run your bot anywhere; on your computer or on a remote server.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702210/extras/46456846c2bf4f5c75da7ab2e6e31a69.webp?t=1692825750\" width=226 height=26 /></span><br>Looking for a rapid development tool for chat bots? Piecewise provides a simple interface - no more syntax errors, no finagling with your environment, no more mess. Build bots of any complexity, click the Play button, and you're online.",
